msgid "LabPlot"
msgstr "LabPlot"

#. (itstool) path: component/summary
#: org.kde.labplot.appdata.xml:15
msgid "Visualize and analyze data"
msgstr "Visualisa e analysa datos"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.labplot.appdata.xml:17
msgid ""
"LabPlot is a FREE, open source and cross-platform Data Visualization and "
"Analysis software accessible to everyone."
msgstr ""
"LabPlot es un software LIBERE e gratuite, a fonte aperite e inter-"
"platteforma per Visualisation e Analyse de datos accessibile a omnes."

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.labplot.appdata.xml:20
msgid ""
"LabPlot provides an easy way to create, manage and edit plots. It allows you "
"to produce plots based on data from a spreadsheet or on data imported from "
"external files. Plots can be exported to several pixmap and vector graphic "
"formats."
msgstr ""
"Labplot forni un modo facile per crear, gerer e modificar tracias (plots). "
"Illo te permitte producer tracias basate sur datos ab un folio electronic o "
"sur datos importate ex files externe. Tracias pote esser exportate a multe "
"formatos de pixmap e vector graphic."

